events.comment: This boss has a shield while his minions are alive. As they are killed, he goes more and more berserk, but when they all die he is left defenseless, even stops attacking. While in this state, a single MELEE attack will destroy the boss

parameters: "Energy from shields partially removed, rerouting power"
"Rerouting energy to guns. Dodge this filthy casual"
"Stop, this energy MUST go somewhere after the shields are down"
"Rerouting power back from energy plates to shield generators..."
"Shields back online. You can't touch this"
